        "rich_text_B7XgR3": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Because your love story deserves more than a ring that just fits",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Because your love story deserves more than a ring that just fits</h2><p>Every relationship is unique, and the ring that marks this beautiful journey of love should be just as unique. Your <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Engagement Ring</span></a> should tell your story, have little secrets that only you and your partner cherish. Your one of a kind custom engagement ring is limited only by your imagination.</p><p>A <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/pages/customized-jewelry\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">custom ring</span></a> doesn’t just give you the creative control to create something different, it lets you create something unique that carries a lot of meaning from the very first sketch. Whether you’re designing it solo for a surprise proposal or creating it together with your partner to create something you both will love, Lucira is here to help you create the ring of your dreams!</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jGKNkG": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Love that Doesn’t Cost ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Love that Doesn’t Cost </h2><p>Love doesn’t harm, it heals. So why should your Engagement Ring come with the guilt of harming the earth we live on? Lucira brings to you an exquisite collection of Lab Grown Diamond Rings that carry the same aesthetic and sentimental value as the traditional Mined Diamonds, but without costing the environment. Unlike Mined Diamonds, our Lab Grown Diamonds don’t cost an arm and a leg. So with Lucira, you get diamonds, but better!</p><p>Now that you know what to choose, here are some ideas to guide you as you start your journey of creating a custom ring for your big day.</p>",
            "custom_id": "love",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Yy8gLR": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1. Start with Your Story",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>1. Start with Your Story</h3>",
            "custom_id": "story",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_c9w6Ty": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Start_with_Your_Story_1000_X_700.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Creating the most perfect ring starts with a great story. Think about what makes your relationship extra special. Is it a place you met, a shared passion, maybe a memory from your first trip together, or simply the little details that define your bond?</p><p>These personal elements can be beautifully woven into the design. For instance:</p><ul><li>A wave-like band to represent beachside memories.</li><li>A secret engraving of a date, place, or word only you two understand.</li><li>A ring made using recycled gold from a family heirloom.</li></ul><p>Let your love story shape the foundation of your design.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "classic-lily-cut-diamond-pendant-necklace",
              "solitaire-diamond-stud-earrings"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_c3ARmc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "2. Choose a Stone that Matches Your Vibe",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>2. Choose a Stone that Matches Your Vibe</h3>",
            "custom_id": "stone",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_DQiHEU": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Choose_a_Stone_that_Matches_Your_Vibe_1000_700_f0623f7e-11a5-4316-b452-3018aa9e0104.jpg",
            "text": "<p>While diamonds are gorgeous in every form, there will always be some that will suit you like no other! So don’t be afraid to explore all the options to find out what matches your vibe the best. While diamonds are the timeless go-to, you could also consider:</p><ul><li>Colored gemstones like sapphires, emeralds, or morganites.</li><li>Birthstones of either partner or a stone from the month you met.</li><li>Salt-and-pepper diamonds for a modern, moody aesthetic.</li></ul>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "1-50-ct-classic-heart-shape-solitaire-ring",
              "1-45-cts-marquise-cut-diamond-engagement-ring",
              "3-928ct-princess-round-diamond-stackable-ring",
              "0-40-ct-aegis-pear-solitaire-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_EAGKRi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "3. Consider the Setting Style",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>3. Consider the Setting Style</h3>",
            "custom_id": "setting",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_taTLw7": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Consider_the_Setting_Style_1000_600_V2.jpg",
            "text": "<p>The setting is what holds your stone in place, and it defines a lot of the ring’s personality. Here are a few popular styles to explore:</p><ul><li>Solitaire: Timeless, simple, and elegant. Perfect if you want the stone to take center stage.</li><li>Halo: A central stone surrounded by a ring of smaller diamonds or gems. It adds extra sparkle and dimension.</li><li>Three-stone: Often said to represent the past, present, and future of a relationship.</li><li>Bezel: The stone is encased in metal. Sleek, modern, and ultra-secure.</li></ul>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_MCGUwQ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "4. Pick a Unique Band Design",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>You can also customize the prongs, use vintage-inspired milgrain detailing, or add hidden accents underneath the setting.</p><h3>4. Pick a Unique Band Design</h3>",
            "custom_id": "band",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_Kj8qRr": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Pick_a_Unique_Band_Design_1000_500.jpg",
            "text": "<p>The band is your canvas, don’t be afraid to get creative with it. Here are a few ways to make it yours:</p><ul><li>Twisted bands to symbolize two lives intertwined.</li><li>Split shanks that give a more dramatic, elegant look.</li><li>Nature-inspired motifs like vines, leaves, or feathers.</li><li>Asymmetrical shapes for an artsy, unexpected edge.</li></ul><p>You can also choose between polished, matte, hammered, or textured finishes for a subtle yet distinct look.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "1-ct-classic-oval-cut-solitaire-ring",
              "0-30-cts-elegant-solitaire-diamond-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_rBPp6k": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "5. Mix Metals for a Contemporary Look",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>5. Mix Metals for a Contemporary Look</h3><p>Who says you have to choose just one metal? Mixing metals, like pairing white gold settings with rose gold accents can add depth and contrast to your design.</p><p>Popular metal choices include:</p><ul><li>Yellow gold settings: Classic and rich.</li><li>White gold or platinum Settings: Cool-toned and modern.</li><li>Rose gold settings: Romantic and warm.</li></ul><p>A dual-tone band, a colored halo, or a contrasting prong can make your ring stand out in a crowd.</p>",
            "custom_id": "metals",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_fP9Lzi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "6. Add a Hidden Detail",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>6. Add a Hidden Detail</h3>",
            "custom_id": "detail",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_3jzYCm": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Add_a_Hidden_Detail_1000_300.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Sometimes the most meaningful parts of a ring are the ones only you and your partner see. A hidden gemstone on the inside of the band. An engraved line from a song. A fingerprint pressed into the metal.</p><p>These subtle touches add an extra layer of intimacy to your design, making your ring truly yours.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "6-05ct-delicate-round-diamond-tennis-bracelet",
              "blue-teardrop-halo-diamond-bracelet"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_H6WL8T": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "7. Involve Your Partner in the Process",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>7. Involve Your Partner in the Process</h3><p>If you’re creating the ring together, treat it like a shared adventure. Visit a jeweler, sketch out ideas, try on sample styles, and talk about your favorite designs. Some couples even attend CAD (computer-aided design) sessions with their jeweler to view 3D renderings before final production.</p><p>Not only does this make the process special, but it also ensures the ring feels right for both of you.</p>",
            "custom_id": "partner",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bLFfQM": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "8. Work with a Designer You Trust",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>8. Work with a Designer You Trust</h3><p>Custom doesn’t have to mean complicated. Many jewelers now specialize in custom pieces and will walk you through each step, from initial consultation to wax modeling to final polishing.</p><p>Choose someone who listens, educates, and respects your budget. If you're working with a brand like Lucira, you’ll also benefit from sustainable practices and ethically sourced, lab grown diamonds that align with your values.</p>",
            "custom_id": "designer",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_gm3zQi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "9. Think Long-Term",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>9. Think Long-Term</h3><p>Finally, remember that your ring is designed for a lifetime. So while it’s great to be creative, also consider wearability, practicality, and how the design might evolve with you over time.</p><p>Would you like it to pair well with a future wedding band? Do you need something low-profile for an <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/sports-collection\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">active lifestyle</span></a>? These questions can help you balance style with function.</p>",
            "custom_id": "longterm",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jNNwJt": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion</h2><p>Designing a custom engagement ring isn’t just about aesthetics, it’s about meaning. It’s the chance to turn your love story into something tangible and timeless, something that lives on your hand and in your heart.</p><p>So take your time, dream big, and design a ring that speaks not just of your love today, but of your forever together.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
